title: Power Slap 8: Da Crazy Hawaiian vs. Van Heerden
overview: Fontainebleau Las Vegas will host the eighth live Power Slap event, Power Slap 8: Da Crazy Hawaiian vs. Van Heerden, on Friday, June 28 at 6PM PT/ 9PM ET and will stream internationally from our 40,000SF Colbalt Ballroom exclusively around the globe on Rumble.
